n><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;68.00 through &#36;78.00</span></span>\n\n\t<div class=\"wd-add-btn wd-add-btn-replace\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product/carnelian-stud-earrings/\" aria-describedby=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23244\" data-quantity=\"1\" class=\"button product_type_variable add_to_cart_button add-to-cart-loop\" data-product_id=\"23244\" data-product_sku=\"\" aria-label=\"Select options for &ldquo;Carnelian Stud Earrings&rdquo;\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"wd-action-icon\"><span class=\"wd-check-icon\"></span></span><span class=\"wd-action-text\">Select options</span></a>\t<span id=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23244\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">\n\t\tThis product has multiple variants. The options may be chosen on the product page\t</span>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ About Crystals for Courage</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can crystals give me courage?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Not directly. Crystals can&#8217;t grant courage. Many people use them as tangible cues to act despite fear; courage is built through practice, not something a stone provides.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are crystals scientifically proven to boost courage?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">No. There is no clinical evidence that crystals increase courage. Any felt benefit usually comes from the ritual of pausing before a brave act, not a proven effect of the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal is best for courage and bravery?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Tiger eye is the most commonly chosen — long tied to courage and steady nerve.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal for the courage to speak up?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Amazonite and carnelian — amazonite for honest words, carnelian for the push to say them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal helps me through a hard, demanding stretch?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Bloodstone and red jasper — bloodstone for backbone, red jasper for courage that lasts.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How should I cleanse courage crystals?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Smoke (sage, palo santo), sound (singing bowl), or moonlight work for most stones. Pyrite is metallic and can tarnish if damp — wipe it dry; handle soft pieces gently.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal bracelet for courage?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A tiger eye bracelet is the most common first choice — durable, widely available, and easy to wear as a steady cue of nerve.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Explore More Crystal Guides</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-confidence/\">Crystals for Confidence</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-protection/\">Crystals for Protection</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-strength/\">Crystals for Strength</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-motivation/\">Crystals for Motivation</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-communication/\">Crystals for Communication</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Courage is moving with the fear still there — and a real stone can be a steady cue to take the step anyway. Start with one and let small brave acts add up. For more, explore <a href=\"/protection-clearing/\">Protection &amp; Clearing</a>.</p>\n",
